block content
	.awfully 
		.container 
			h1(data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-once="true"  data-aos-delay="100")
				span Awfully
				span English Vodka
			.awfully__subtitle(data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-once="true" data-aos-delay="200") For Quintessentially English Pleasures 
			.awfully__mainImg-mob(data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-once="true" data-aos-delay="500")
				img(src="img/awfully/item1.png", alt="")
			.awfully__descr(data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-once="true" data-aos-delay="400"  data-aos-offset="-300") Broken Clock comes from the abundant English country garden at Shandy Hall in North Yorkshire – a place which was once the home to England’s Most Eccentric author, Laurence Sterne – and where time seems to stand still.
			.awfully__mainImg(data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-once="true" data-aos-delay="500")
				img(src="img/awfully/item1.png", alt="")
			.awfully__descr(data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-once="true") 
				p The very same essences of Englishness can be found in Broken Clock – a Sophisticated yet Playful spirit which is crafted by time in the North of England sing
				p It is an indubitably apt vodka to pour for the most Awfully English of tipples, from a Bloody Mary at brunch or afternoon drinks on the terrace to a Broken Clock martini by moonlight in your own English Country Garden.
			.awfully__imgList.swiper 
				.swiper-wrapper 
					.swiper-slide.awfully__img(data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-once="true")
						img(src="img/awfully/item2.jpeg", alt="")
					.swiper-slide.awfully__img(data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-once="true")
						img(src="img/awfully/item3.jpeg", alt="")
					.swiper-slide.awfully__img(data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-once="true")
						img(src="img/awfully/item4.jpeg", alt="")
				.swiper-pagination.awfully__pagination